{"tid":1168361,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做左1年recruitment consultant  **你問我答","createTime":"2019-05-23T15:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T03:22:35.000Z","uid":255160,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"51f0092b7d0cd825e623bcd5f406706ff0a35306","tid":1168361,"uid":255160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"唔經唔覺都做左一年recruitment consultant ，當中真係見過好多千其百趣既人，亦好多辛酸史<br />\n<br />\n大家俾我呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢星期真係好唔順，其實我都只係想請retail sales，但上到黎個個都話想搵份坐既SALES，坦白講除左CALL CENTER同金行,賣錶SALES有得坐下之外，我都諗唔到邊份SALES可以坐。我地呢行真係好講運，除左搵人難，未到最後一刻個CAN 返工，我地都唔會有錢收。好多時簽好約但最後no show，所有心血就白廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實做我地呢行唔係真係剩係SELL個CAN俾個客，我地既責任係幫佢地點樣可以搵到自己既路，同點準備好佢地自己。好多人誤解左，當然我認，做呢行就係為左份佣，但錢背後要講良心。唔係3721就塞D唔岩既工俾個客，人地都唔想做果行，上到去就HARD SELL D工俾人，有乜意思"},{"pid":"ec3194ffb8ce15e08dccd2df324fabaa1f391db2","tid":1168361,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"點計佣？"},{"pid":"a573f576776002a75c92e8dc0d88ba1c4bda958d","tid":1168361,"uid":224479,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"其實咁好意思叫自己做consultant:o<br />\nagent 就 agent"},{"pid":"a3e3a91df276b305ff2490b4283f6e4aa4ff85a0","tid":1168361,"uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78caecf76d18bff66aefe1ab1c7af66d422ada29","tid":1168361,"uid":105958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"RETAIL 都要搵AGENT?<br />\n你地係唔係真係幫人叫高D人工<br />\n定昆人張CV或者跑CAN INTERVIEW 數"},{"pid":"fc4dec4695f8c764dd9ed9248305fc33c4527dc9","tid":1168361,"uid":157913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"做咩level嘅位 junior? Mid to senior? Executive?<br />\n專做perm 位？contrac